{
  "stem": "9701.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's when I began to experience anti-Semitism in school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "However, I was aware of anti-Semitism prior to that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the first thing was when Hitler came to power on January 30, 1933, I remember my parents and other adults talking about Hitler and saying that they hoped his regime wouldn't last, that he was a bad person.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't, at that time, really think it had very much to do with me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just thought it was some adults talking a lot of nonsense.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But just two months later, on Saturday, April 1, 1933, I realized that perhaps it did indeed have something to do with me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because on that day, there was a boycott of Jewish businesses all over Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The purpose of the boycott was to prevent Christians from shopping in Jewish stores.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as I mentioned earlier, my father had a store.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I recall that there was a Nazi standing in front of my father's business.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Another one was standing in front of the Jewish butcher, the Jewish bakery, the Jewish hardware store.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I asked my father, what is this all about?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, you know, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It'll go away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And indeed, it did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That boycott lasted only that one day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "However, there were long-range repercussions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because after that, Christians were afraid to shop in Jewish stores.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so there were economic repercussions, which I sort of sensed in terms of that maybe be things were a little more difficult financially for my family, though it was never talked about.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I think I sort of picked it up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I remember on a building right across from where my father's business was, there was a glass case, which displayed one of the Nazi newspapers.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
